{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Protocol","externalID":"s:15SpooktacularKit12ScreenReaderP","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ScreenReader"}],"modules":[{"name":"SpooktacularKit"}],"symbolKind":"protocol","role":"symbol","title":"ScreenReader","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ScreenReader","kind":"identifier"}]},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/screenreader"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ScreenReader","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ScreenReader","kind":"identifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s8SendableP","text":"Sendable","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Implement this protocol to provide screen capture and OCR"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for screen-aware Setup Assistant automation. The screen reader"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"enables the automation executor to wait for specific text to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"appear on the VM display before proceeding, replacing fixed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"timing delays with deterministic screen state checks."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Design","anchor":"Design"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This follows the approach used by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/cirruslabs\/tart"